 DemoGridFormat connected;values;F;colTitles;rowTitles;cellWidths;cellTypes;g
 EWC.CONNECTED‚Üêconnected
 ‚éïPW‚Üê1000

‚çù Grid FormatString Demo
‚çù Showcases ‚éïFMT formatting: commas, currency, custom boolean text, padding

 F‚Üê'F1'
 F eWC'Form' 'Grid ‚éïFMT Formatting'(50 50)(520 800)('Coord' 'Pixel')

‚çù Financial data: 7 rows √ó 6 columns ‚Äî numbers big enough to show comma separators
‚çù Company | Revenue ($) | Employees | Status | Growth | Sector
 values‚Üê7 6‚ç¥‚ç¨
 values[1;]‚Üê'Axiom'        8500000  8500 1  23.4  'Technology'
 values[2;]‚Üê'Boltzmann'   42000000 31000 1   1.5  'Legacy'
 values[3;]‚Üê'Cantor'       1250000  1200 0  ¬Ø8.7  'Consulting'
 values[4;]‚Üê'Dirichlet'   15750000 14500 1  15.6  'Finance'
 values[5;]‚Üê'Euler'        3200000  2800 1   8.9  'Technology'
 values[6;]‚Üê'Fibonacci'   97500000 52000 1  31.2  'Data'
 values[7;]‚Üê'Gauss'        6800000  6300 0  ¬Ø4.2  'Finance'

 colTitles‚Üê'Company' 'Revenue ($)' 'Headcount' 'Status' 'Growth %' 'Sector'
 rowTitles‚Üê‚ç≥7
 cellWidths‚Üê110 130 90 120 100 90

‚çù Create the Grid
 g‚ÜêF,'.G'
 g eWC'Grid'('Posn'(80 20))('Size'(134 673))('Values' values)('ColTitles' colTitles)('RowTitles' rowTitles)('CellWidths' cellWidths)('TitleWidth' 30)('CurCell'(1 1))('VScroll' ¬Ø1)

‚çù Input components ‚Äî one per column type
 (g,'.E1')eWC'Edit'                          ‚çù 1: Company name (text)
 (g,'.E2')eWC'Edit'('FieldType' 'Numeric')   ‚çù 2: Revenue (large currency)
 (g,'.E3')eWC'Edit'('FieldType' 'Numeric')   ‚çù 3: Headcount (integer)
 (g,'.B1')eWC'Button'('Style' 'Check')('Caption' '')  ‚çù 4: Status (checkbox ‚Äî toggle-able)
 (g,'.E4')eWC'Edit'('FieldType' 'Numeric')   ‚çù 5: Growth (percentage)
 (g,'.L2')eWC'Label'                         ‚çù 6: Sector (read-only)

 g eWS'Input'((g,'.E1')(g,'.E2')(g,'.E3')(g,'.B1')(g,'.E4')(g,'.L2'))
 cellTypes‚Üê7 6‚ç¥1 2 3 4 5 6
 g eWS'CellTypes' cellTypes

‚çù FormatString ‚Äî one per CellType:
‚çù 1: ''                                     plain text (Company)
‚çù 2: 'CF15.2'                               currency with commas  (8500000 ‚Üí "  8,500,000.00")
‚çù 3: 'CI8'                                  integer with commas   (8500 ‚Üí "   8,500")
‚çù 4: 'O0<LOSS-MAKING>O1<PROFITABLE >I14'    boolean ‚Üí custom text
‚çù 5: 'F8.1'                                 fixed-point, 1 decimal
‚çù 6: ''                                     plain text (Sector)
 g eWS'FormatString'('' 'CF15.2' 'CI8' 'O0<LOSS-MAKING>O1<PROFITABLE >I14' 'F8.1' '')

‚çù ShowInput only affects Combo/Button cells (‚éïWC); Edit/Numeric/Label cells
‚çù ignore it. Here every column shows its ‚éïFMT-formatted text and edits on
‚çù select ‚Äî so ShowInput is 0 throughout.
 g eWS'ShowInput' 0

‚çù Events
 g eWS'Event'(‚äÇ'CellMove' 'CBGrid')
 g eWS'Event'(‚äÇ'CellChanged' 'CBGrid')

‚çù Header labels explaining the formatting
 (F,'.Title')eWC'Label' 'Grid FormatString ‚Äî Server-side ‚éïFMT Formatting'(10 20)(20 750)
 (F,'.Info1')eWC'Label' 'Revenue: CF15.2 ‚Üí 8,500,000.00    Headcount: CI8 ‚Üí 8,500    Status: O-format ‚Üí PROFITABLE'(30 20)(20 750)
 (F,'.Info2')eWC'Label' 'All formatting done by ‚éïFMT on the server. Edit a numeric cell & blur to see it re-format.'(50 20)(20 750)

‚çù Event log
 (F,'.LogTitle')eWC'Label' 'Event Log:'(310 20)(20 100)
 (F,'.Log')eWC'Label' '(Events will appear here)'(330 20)(160 750)
